        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Veterans' Telecommunication Protection Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires a cable or voice service provider to charge a veterans' organization at an individual or household service rate unless that rate is greater than the amount the provider would otherwise charge the organization.</p>]]>
        </text>
